OL,6,     FJustin and Charlie host at the
OL,7,     FArtist Residence in Penzance. Most
OL,8,     Fof their guests like the quirky,
OL,9,     Fart-filled rooms, but a
OL,10,     Fhair-raising shower dampens some
OL,11,     Fspirits.
