OL,5,G1615 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FAt The Grange Boutique Hotel in
OL,7,     FCumbria, Jackie and Nigel hope to
OL,8,     Fimpress with high-end suites. But
OL,9,     FSimon finds his room stifling and
OL,10,     Fthe breakfast eggs aren't all
OL,11,     Fthey're cracked up to be.
OL,12,G1650 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FThe second visit is to Ruth and
OL,14,     FLucy's Rutland Luxury Lodges in
OL,15,     FGreetham. Most of their guests
OL,16,     Ffind luxury in abundance, but
OL,17,     FJackie and Nigel get hot and
OL,18,     Fbothered about the bedding.
