OL,5,G1720 Four in a Bed
OL,6,     FThe third visit is to The
OL,7,     FLeicester Arms in Kent, hosted by
OL,8,     Fhusbands Laurence and Danny. Some
OL,9,     Fguests get a spotless welcome, but
OL,10,     FJackie and Nigel make dirty
OL,11,     Fdiscoveries.
OL,12,G1750 Four in a Bed
OL,13,     FThe final visit is to Oakover
OL,14,     FGuest House in Weston-super-Mare,
OL,15,     Fhosted by Simon Robinson and Ann
OL,16,     FWilson. The B&Bers are delighted
OL,17,     Fby the decor, but Lucy and Ruth
OL,18,     Fget a frosty reception...
